				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Already been said, but just to reiterate...without back off you're not clearing present hate list. It's the same thing if your pet is engaging a mob (say you're clearing greens one immediately after the other) and you target the next victim and hit pet attack (so there's no downtime between killings). Your pet doesn't immediately switch targets. If you wanted to switch targets, you'd have to back off and attack the new mob. Same thing here, except you're inserting hold.
<br />

<br />
Opt</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
