			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Had a situation last night that illustrates the "unreliability" issue with the pets. Two mobs, well spaced (side and "near clock" of Phase 1/2 trial area, for those familiar). Pet was on one, used hotkey:
<br />

<br />
/pet hold
<br />
/pause 10, /pet report health
<br />
/pet back off
<br />

<br />
targetted other, /pet attack -- pet went back to the original mob. No AoEs or low-health aggro involved.
<br />

<br />
To my knowledge, it is not repeatable; it just occasionally happens.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=568700" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
